  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Designing Awesome Tracks**\n\nI\'m now focusing on `/src/data.ts` and the variables for tracks, services, and testimonials. I\'ve shifted gears to designing impressive-sounding tracks. My plan is a sequencer-based Web Audio synth, capable of playing sequences customized to track properties. The goal is awesome tracks!\n\n\n**Defining Track Properties**\n\nI\'m now detailing track properties for `/src/data.ts`. I\'ve outlined three tracks: \"Neo-Tokyo Drive\" (Cyberpunk), \"Solaris Reflection\" (Ambient), and \"Sunset Grid\" (Synthwave). For each, I\'m specifying genre, BPM, key, color, base frequency, and a descriptive paragraph in Spanish. I\'m focusing on crafting a rich dataset for these tracks.\n\n\n**Cataloging Studio Services**\n\nI\'m now cataloging our studio services within `/src/data.ts`. I\'m including detailed descriptions and specifications for \"Full Production,\" \"Mixing,\" and \"Mastering.\" I\'m also focusing on key attributes like \"Icon\", \"Features,\" \"Duration,\" \"GlowColor,\" and \"Badge\" to ensure all services are clearly defined, categorized, and visually appealing.\n\n\n**Refining Mastering Details**\n\nI\'m refining the \"Mastering\" service entry in `/src/data.ts`. I\'ve updated the icon choices and meticulously crafted a compelling Spanish description. I\'m focusing on features such as \"Digital & Analog precision mastering,\" high-quality dithering, ISRC metadata, and optimizations for Spotify and Apple Music. Now, I\'m defining some outstanding testimonials from famous artists, like Valerya and Marcus Thorne, to provide credibility.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I will now create `/src/data.ts` to keep our static configurations separate from UI code. This includes our customizable high-tech tracks, industry-standard production services with glowing accent colors, and stellar artist testimonials."
    thinking_duration {
