    modified_response: "I will write the `/src/components/ContactForm.tsx` component. It implements an exquisite, highly interactive conversational booking board. It guides the client step-by-step with elegant animated gates rather than forcing them to stare at a cold grid:\n1. **Name Prompt**: Captures the artist\'s name.\n2. **Dynamic Service Selection**: Provides custom service selection cards.\n3. **Budget Target Range**: Offers preset professional scales.\n4. **Email Capture**: Gathers contact handles.\n5. **Simulated Telemetry Gateway**: Toggling submission launches a stylized, glowing terminal log showing data compilation traces (\"Inyectando propuesta... Completado\") before displaying a friendly confirmation card."
